# INHERITANCE
          Kalıtım

          Types of Inheritance
          - Single Inheritance
          - Multiple Inheritance
          - Multilevel Inheritance
          - Hierarchical Inheritance
          - Hybrid Inheritance


                                         -----> Class C
                                        |
          Class A -----> Class B ----->
                                        |
                                         -----> Class D

                         -------------------------------> Hierarchical Inheritance
          -----------------------> Single Inheritance 



                                ------------------------------> Multiple Inheritance

                         -----> Class B ---->
                        |                    |
          Class A ----->                       -----> Class D
                        |                    |
                         -----> Class C ---->

          -----------------------------> Hierarchical Inheritance
          ----------------------------------------------------> Hybrid Inheritance


          -------------------------------------> Multilevel Inheritance
          Class A -----> Class B -----> Class A 


